<i>adjective</i>: 따끔따끔하다 [따끔따끔하다], 따갑다 [따갑따], 껄끄럽다 [껄끄럽따] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>따끔따끔하다 [따끔따끔하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. smarting</dd><br>
<dd>따가울 정도로 몹시 덥다.</dd><br>
<dd>To be very hot, giving a smarting feeling.</dd><br>
<dd>2. prickly</dd><br>
<dd>마음의 자극을 받아 자꾸 찔리는 듯한 느낌이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>To have a guilty feeling continuously that stimulates one's heart.</dd><br>
<dd>3. painful</dd><br>
<dd>찔리거나 꼬집히는 것처럼 자꾸 따갑게 아프다.</dd><br>
<dd>To have a hurtful feeling like being poked or pinched continuously.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>따갑다 [따갑따]</dt><br>
<dd>1. scorching; sultry</dd><br>
<dd>살갗이 따끔거릴 만큼 덥다.</dd><br>
<dd>So hot the skin feels like it is on fire.</dd><br>
<dd>2. prickly; pricking</dd><br>
<dd>살을 찌르는 것처럼 아프다.</dd><br>
<dd>Aching as if the skin is pricked.</dd><br>
<dd>3. scorching; harsh</dd><br>
<dd>눈길이나 충고 등이 매우 비판적이고 날카롭다.</dd><br>
<dd>Advice or a glare, etc., being very critical and sharp.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>껄끄럽다 [껄끄럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>1. prickly</dd><br>
<dd>뻣뻣한 것이 몸에 닿아서 따가운 느낌이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having a prickling sensation when something stiff touches one's body.</dd><br>
<dd>2. coarse</dd><br>
<dd>미끄럽지 못하고 거칠다.</dd><br>
<dd>Rough, not smooth and silky.</dd><br>
<dd>3. uncomfortable</dd><br>
<dd>마음에 썩 내키지 않고 매우 불편한 데가 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling reluctant and uncomfortable.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>